'''Tamaziɣt n watlas Ablidi''', (ⵜⴰⵛⴻⵍⵃⵉⵜ ⵏ ⵡⴰⵜⵍⴰⵙ ⴰⴱⵍⵉⴷⵉ) d tutlayt i ttmeslayen [[iamaziɣen n watlas Ablidi]]. Tamaziɣt n watlas Ablidi tettikki deg tutlayin timaziɣin. Ma ɣas tutlayt [[tamaziɣt]], zik, tettwaru s isekkilen n [[tifinaɣ]] akken tettwaru tmaceɣt ar wass-a, tamaziɣt n tmurt n watlas Ablidi tettwaru nettat s isekkilen ilatiniyen.
